01:27:49,014 --> 01:27:52,017
<i>Lihat tampang sombong di wajah sombongnya.</i>

1276
01:27:52,100 --> 01:27:53,518
<i>Dia pikir kita pasangan.</i>

1277
01:27:55,061 --> 01:27:57,147
<i>Dia pikir kita punya hubungan.</i>

1278
01:27:57,230 --> 01:28:00,734
